Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.52,0:01:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就以自己的身體\N來體會我的救世之正確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.46,0:01:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.56,0:02:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.67,0:02:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,南無阿彌陀佛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.47,0:02:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢著 現在念佛還太早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.24,0:02:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.98,0:02:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二重極被避開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.37,0:02:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第四十八話\N救世的再生 安慈的新出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.28,0:02:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉 贏是贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.74,0:02:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但好像是湊巧獲勝的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.71,0:02:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我是故意保留\N最後的二重極的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.49,0:02:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直接命中他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.42,0:02:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然他沒有死…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.50,0:03:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.52,0:03:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牌位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.42,0:03:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到他來決鬥\N還把牌位藏在胸前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.75,0:03:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.92,0:03:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是未受拯救的\N心靈純淨的人的靈魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.23,0:03:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切始於十年前\N廢佛毀釋那一年…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.31,0:03:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿  那是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.38,0:04:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要  還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.42,0:04:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太助 別欺負吾郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.15,0:04:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吾郎 你也別為了小事哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.42,0:04:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們的水還沒有打完呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.16,0:04:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.69,0:04:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安慈和尚也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.96,0:04:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生氣的時候一定要狠下心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.17,0:04:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老是那麼溫柔是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.00,0:04:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我不擅長生氣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.01,0:04:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼呀 你的長相\N已經比一般人柔弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.78,0:04:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不兇一點怎麼行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.15,0:04:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.45,0:04:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.75,0:04:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,椿姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.05,0:04:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼啦 這次又是什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.82,0:04:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪跑到背裏面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.79,0:04:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們到底在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.22,0:04:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個叫做佛祖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.73,0:04:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛祖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.40,0:04:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和尚 你看 寫好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.70,0:04:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽好了  你們的爸爸媽媽\N都到很遠的地方去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.77,0:04:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是佛祖隨時都會保佑你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.27,0:05:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.78,0:05:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他會聽到你們的祈禱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.11,0:05:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那祈禱的話  我會長高嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.68,0:05:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,春天會早點來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.55,0:05:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會娶姐姐嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.99,0:05:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和尚 我們會祈禱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.13,0:05:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你願意娶小椿姐姐嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.33,0:05:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你  拜託啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.46,0:05:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傻瓜 你們在胡說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.13,0:05:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家再去祈禱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.40,0:05:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些小孩都那麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.37,0:05:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以為我嫁給您以後\N大家就能成為真正的家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.41,0:05:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,家人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.75,0:05:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是您的贈禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.79,0:05:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的寶物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.43,0:05:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要拆掉這家寺院？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.50,0:06:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明治政府定下了\N廢佛毀釋的方針
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.37,0:06:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這件事你知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.04,0:06:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收到命令後\N大家集會決定拆毀這座寺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.18,0:06:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是無所謂 但那些孩子的\N父親在戌辰戰爭中喪生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.45,0:06:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無處可歸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.78,0:06:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些小鬼\N就是這個村子的掃把星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.96,0:06:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們的父親在戌辰戰爭時\N給幕府出力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.66,0:06:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,害得我們村子到現在\N還被明治政府視為眼中釘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.13,0:06:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於那些掃把星\N我們才永遠收不到錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.87,0:06:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你們馬上離開這村子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.11,0:06:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,村長  這麼軟弱的說詞有用嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.32,0:06:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對方是沒半個信徒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.79,0:06:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破寺廟的和尚\N跟無父無母的髒小鬼哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.76,0:06:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管受到怎樣對待\N也沒有人替他們主持公道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.13,0:06:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明治政府的恩惠\N分配上是有限的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.70,0:07:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再慢吞吞的話\N好處都會被別的村子搶走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.04,0:07:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和尚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.84,0:07:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寺廟會被拆掉嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.07,0:07:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會被趕出去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.58,0:07:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們已經很拚命在祈禱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.55,0:07:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 和尚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.88,0:07:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我爸爸的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.49,0:07:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用道歉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.16,0:07:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你們的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.59,0:07:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是為了早點讓和平\N來到這時代而奉獻犧牲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.10,0:07:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家不用擔心什麼\N只要想著如何幸福就成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.50,0:07:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是你們過世的父母們的願望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.77,0:07:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是我的願望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.08,0:07:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然留在這裏\N會給其他村人添麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.85,0:07:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們看怎樣\N大家一起搬去新的地方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.22,0:07:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們喜歡哪裏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.92,0:08:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去東京  東京最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.96,0:08:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想去京都  我要去函館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.43,0:08:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,函館那裏正在打仗  很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.87,0:08:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無聊  那麼哪裏好呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.57,0:08:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛啊 這些孩子們\N過去吃了太多苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.94,0:08:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請您給予他們幸福的未來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.61,0:08:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請您保佑這些孩子們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.19,0:08:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,睡不著嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.26,0:08:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 吵醒你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.57,0:08:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要擔心 我會努力工作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.84,0:08:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會比大人差的\N我可以幫上您的忙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.44,0:08:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.28,0:08:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝 我們是家人\N團結起來沒有辦不到的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.02,0:09:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛祖在看守著我們的\N你就放心地去睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.42,0:09:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛祖啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.79,0:09:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請保護我們一家人 拜託…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.99,0:09:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小椿、吾郎、太助 大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.09,0:09:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.40,0:09:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就解決掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.23,0:09:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰叫你不早點滾蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.54,0:09:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就可以\N得到明治政府的恩惠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.01,0:10:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛啊 這些孩子們\N過去吃了太多苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.32,0:10:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請您給予他們幸福的未來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.12,0:10:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請您保佑這些孩子們  保佑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.47,0:10:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼  為什麼這些孩子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.21,0:11:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我錯了  五年前的事 我錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.01,0:11:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求求你 饒我一命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.76,0:11:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,南無…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.56,0:11:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,南無阿彌陀佛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.59,0:11:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解了嗎 祈禱與許願\N什麼都沒辦法拯救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.22,0:11:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.16,0:12:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這些孩子經由輪迴\N再次轉生到這世間之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.50,0:12:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明王安慈絕不能輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.08,0:12:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切都是為了救世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.11,0:12:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了拯救這個難以拯救的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.98,0:12:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明王安慈絕不能輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.09,0:12:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.66,0:12:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.53,0:12:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.56,0:12:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.19,0:12:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.36,0:13:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 一樣 都一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.93,0:13:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就是那時候的我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.67,0:13:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.94,0:13:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以滿腔的恨意\N以恨來追悼心愛的人的死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.12,0:13:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是沒遇到劍心\N我永遠不會察覺到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.72,0:13:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己已經成為\N只有恨意的醜惡男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.46,0:13:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟現在的你一樣\N是骯髒污穢的怨念的集合體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.47,0:13:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口 你什麼都不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.26,0:14:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事 兩人都\N使出一擊必倒的二重極
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.60,0:14:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼到現在都沒人倒下呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.24,0:14:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們倆現在倒下去\N是一點也不奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.64,0:14:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,促使兩人不斷出拳的\N是那股絕不認輸的意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.95,0:14:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如今精神已經凌駕他們肉體了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.69,0:14:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雙方的二重極\N都無法成為決勝關鍵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.05,0:14:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來是不分勝負了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.59,0:14:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這麼認為嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.66,0:14:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖說他被算進十本刀之內\N可是卻不是劍客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.00,0:14:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 為什麼他要佩劍呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.59,0:15:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遠隔攻擊（遠當）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.02,0:15:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.76,0:15:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將劍插入地面使出二重極\N藉此傳導衝擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.93,0:15:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那把劍是間接攻擊的道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.50,0:15:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下子勝負分出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.36,0:15:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跑到攻擊距離之外\N那烏頭小子就無法攻擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.75,0:15:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被看穿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.55,0:15:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經夠了  安慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.82,0:15:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你活得很辛苦 傷痕纍纍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.33,0:15:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏為滿是創傷的人生\N打上休止符吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.80,0:16:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傷痕纍纍無所謂\N我已經感覺不到痛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.07,0:16:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要成為明王繼續戰下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.04,0:16:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直到我救世成功\N的日子來臨為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.08,0:16:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是那些孩子希望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.45,0:16:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.85,0:16:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孩子們根本不指望你當明王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.22,0:16:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看\N他們被你的鮮血染濕在哭呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.70,0:16:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和尚  已經沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.84,0:16:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 腳還會痛嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.41,0:16:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是有點扭到而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.41,0:16:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係 你別動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.38,0:16:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果時間能夠停住\N不知道該多好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.25,0:16:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後大家\N就可以永遠保持現在生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.16,0:16:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,活在幸福之中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.46,0:17:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算長大了  不管發生什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.00,0:17:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都要留在你身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.10,0:17:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永遠與和尚在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.14,0:17:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.34,0:17:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有那個資格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.51,0:17:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我殺人 奪走了…許多生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.93,0:17:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和尚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.86,0:17:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和尚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.53,0:17:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有次你不是告訴我們嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.70,0:17:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論是悲傷還是憎恨\N佛都會原諒我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.11,0:17:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是你教過我們的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.14,0:17:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們永遠跟和尚在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.55,0:17:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永遠在一起 一直在您身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.05,0:17:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直在你旁邊  一直…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.29,0:18:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說是吧 和尚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.47,0:18:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和尚 快殺死他\N快給他斃命一擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.02,0:18:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的眼神跟剛才不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.75,0:18:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是殺人的眼神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.96,0:18:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就夠了\N恢復成原來那好心的和尚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.76,0:18:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再度救世吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.50,0:18:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人沒那麼簡單\N光靠善心就能拯救…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.40,0:18:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這件事十年前我就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.60,0:18:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你牌位上的孩子們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.77,0:18:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直到死前一刻\N都是被你的善心所救不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.41,0:18:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了那些孩子們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.75,0:19:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不該死在這裏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.09,0:19:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過去…過去我錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.00,0:19:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.07,0:19:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 是你贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.10,0:19:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贏是贏了  可是很辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.41,0:19:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連根手指都動不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.81,0:19:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思 你們先走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.98,0:19:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我休息一下再追上你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.59,0:19:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.26,0:19:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一位選手脫離戰線了\N我們趕路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.96,0:19:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.53,0:19:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趕回去葵屋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.17,0:20:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前面的十本刀\N只有宗次郎、宇水、方治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.84,0:20:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他人都去葵屋殺人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.11,0:20:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.15,0:20:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢著 你別誤會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.69,0:20:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個計劃是方治提議的\N不是志志雄的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.42,0:20:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣都行  向前進吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.43,0:20:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是無法走回頭路的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.43,0:20:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迷路的話 你是保證死定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.37,0:20:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.37,0:20:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快走吧\N這應該比在迷宮中迷路快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.08,0:20:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有帶藥嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.02,0:20:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有 在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.08,0:20:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留下來吧 我來治療他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.62,0:20:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.79,0:20:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快走吧  好了  帶路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.20,0:20:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師父 拜託 一定要趕上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.92,0:21:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行  四周被完全包圍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.52,0:21:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人數大約150人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.56,0:21:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.57,0:21:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了  這是第二個房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.54,0:21:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦打開這扇門\N就無法抽身了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.34,0:21:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必口述了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.38,0:21:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇水 你在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.75,0:21:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.49,0:21:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是 吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.14,0:22:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.60,0:22:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.11,0:22:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別喊得那麼親近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.94,0:22:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是志志雄死後\N連舔我腳趾都不夠格的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.55,0:22:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄死後？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.75,0:22:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦 只有兩個人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.69,0:22:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧 就當作是\N殺死志志雄前的試刀會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.26,0:22:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說吧  你們誰想先下黃泉呢

